OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering his
OL,4,Cdaughter-in-law
OL,6,FA man from Wigan who murdered his
OL,7,Fdaughter-in-law six months after she
OL,8,Fcame to the UK to marry his son has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for life.
OL,11,FNadeem Begum, 53, told police he'd
OL,12,Ffound Mashal Ilyas, 24, unconscious at
OL,13,Fthe bottom of the stairs at the family
OL,14,Fhome in Oxford Road, Atherton.
OL,16,FThey were the only people in the house
OL,17,Fat the time and he suggested she must
OL,18,Fhave fallen while he was asleep.
