OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering his
OL,4,Cdaughter-in-law
OL,6,FBut a post mortem found Mashal had a
OL,7,Fnumber of injuries including bruising
OL,8,Fto her neck that were not consistent
OL,9,Fwith a fall and that she died from
OL,10,Fasphyxiation.
OL,12,FTwo spots of Begum's blood were found
OL,13,Fon her trousers and his DNA was also
OL,14,Frecovered from under her fingernails.
OL,16,FA jury at Manchester Crown Court found
OL,17,Fhim guilty of murder and today he was
OL,18,Fhanded a life sentence with a minimum
OL,19,Fterm of 18-years.
