OL,6,FThe court heard during the trial that
OL,7,Fthere were tensions in the family,
OL,8,Fparticularly between Mashal and Begum
OL,9,Fand his views on her role within the
OL,10,Fhousehold.
OL,12,FShe'd come to the UK following wedding
OL,13,Farrangements made by the two families.
OL,15,FDuncan Thorpe, senior investigating
OL,16,Fofficer, said: "This was a brutal and
OL,17,Funprovoked attack on a young woman who
OL,18,Fhad come to the UK to start a new life.
