OL,6,F"Begum now has to face the
OL,7,Fconsequences; we are pleased we have
OL,8,Fbeen able to bring justice and some
OL,9,Fform of closure for the family."
OL,11,FMashal's mother Rehana said her
OL,12,Fdaughter was a 'young woman who had
OL,13,Fher whole life in front of her'.
