OL,6,F"I wonder how she would have grown as
OL,7,Fa woman and a mother and who she would
OL,8,Fhave become, the children she would
OL,9,Fhave had, the memories she would have
OL,10,Fmade, the challenges she would have
OL,11,Fovercome and the joy and happiness
OL,12,Fthat would have filled her life, " she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"But I will never have that chance to
OL,16,Fsee this because Nadeem Begum took
OL,17,Fthat away from her in one senseless
OL,18,Fmoment."
